    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, players must navigate through a randomly generated map using a Lidar scanner, which helps them visualize the environment in real time. The Lidar scanner reveals nearby obstacles, pathways, and hidden dangers as it sweeps across the terrain.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215800/extras/5576c477ae61371810fb4f286ba4d451.poster.avif?t=1732826230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215800/extras/5576c477ae61371810fb4f286ba4d451.webm?t=1732826230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215800/extras/5576c477ae61371810fb4f286ba4d451.mp4?t=1732826230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, there's an ever-present threat: a relentless enemy that hunts the player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215800/extras/63036bff0c155e76d5d17a05a57d82b9.poster.avif?t=1732826230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215800/extras/63036bff0c155e76d5d17a05a57d82b9.webm?t=1732826230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215800/extras/63036bff0c155e76d5d17a05a57d82b9.mp4?t=1732826230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players must constantly move, scanning their surroundings to find escape routes or hiding spots while being chased. The tension escalates as the enemy grows more persistent, forcing players to think quickly and react based on the Lidar's feedback.<br>You can also change the texture and sound of the enemy to your own.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215800/extras/41cc29eb972bfd6ca171ed6579004c41.poster.avif?t=1732826230\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215800/extras/41cc29eb972bfd6ca171ed6579004c41.webm?t=1732826230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215800/extras/41cc29eb972bfd6ca171ed6579004c41.mp4?t=1732826230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
